{"tid":784103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「最終有您」犬掌印出錯　狗主留憾","createTime":"2018-08-18T06:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T06:37:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dfaa276082a1c63425276dd6c229ed2e5b754690","tid":784103,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:05:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180818/20479153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180818%2F20479153&d=n%2F1b9%2BlpRibGc%2B7vlEcTXDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=20701d7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180818%2F20479153&h=8925fe19\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180818/20479153</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月18日 <br />\n<br />\n「最終有您」犬掌印出錯　狗主留憾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180818/large/a0804a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180818%2Flarge%2Fa0804a.gif&h=cc599bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Carol訂製愛犬的立體手印（上圖），但貨不對辦。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「可惜狗狗屍體已經火化，唔可以再留掌印做模型啦！」今年2月女狗主Carol養了15年的北京狗「枕頭」心臟病發去世，她向寵物善終公司訂製3D立體手印。上周家人取來手印製成品，發現欠立體感，質疑有人出錯，涉事公司道歉，願意退款，但Carol沒法為愛犬留掌印紀念已成永遠遺憾。她質疑有人違反商品說明條例，已向海關投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180818/large/a0804b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180818%2Flarge%2Fa0804b.gif&h=42d69c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n製作需時半年<br />\n<br />\n現時在澳洲珀斯工作假期的Carol稱，枕頭是隻北京狗，已經15歲，小六那年爸爸將剛滿月的枕頭送給她，「佢由我讀小六開始，到我中學畢業出嚟社會做嘢，都一直陪住我」。她說枕頭不只是寵物，更是朋友家人。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月大年初一，Carol帶枕頭到寵物美容院剪毛扮靚靚，職員發覺牠喘氣，Carol於是帶枕頭求診，醫護懷疑牠心臟病發，當晚Carol帶枕頭回家休息，豈料翌日枕頭暴斃。Carol找寵物善終公司「最終有您」辦後事，兩周後舉行火化儀式，當日支付980元替愛犬訂購手印永留紀念。<br />\n<br />\nCarol於6月赴澳，本想帶同愛犬手印同去，但善終公司指製作需時半年，直至上周由家人取貨。她收到手印照片後，發現製成品欠立體感，並取出枕頭照片比對，發現不似真掌印，於是越洋致電善終公司追究。<br />\n<br />\nCarol稱對方指事件出錯，願意退款，但要求她交回掌印。她質疑有關公司違反商品說明條例，已向海關投訴事件。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向「最終有您」查詢，姓陳職員就事件致歉，他解釋，手印是另一間公司製造，他稱接獲盧小姐投訴後已向製作公司了解，對方稱「我哋留個模留得唔好」，他指經過今次事件，會考慮停止提供立體手印服務。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林熊、關英傑  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n日曾關代代木公園<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n雪橇狗暴瘦甩毛　扎鐵工虐畜候懲"},{"pid":"67460a33ba9124020a57cfdcb0364c6bad47a89c","tid":784103,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":14,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:09:42.000Z","msg":"寵物撚寧舍戇鳩 搞咩善終呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8468c26c9e9aea7659376587fbc50a1167698992","tid":784103,"uid":22624,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:12:44.000Z","msg":"唔緊要，等我做Carol 隻狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55197b89163765a99dec141e888d4fd4e9ea451e","tid":784103,"uid":28563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:19:00.000Z","msg":"留名睇0愛心child登仔屌人戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571f4f5b4aba2a34db7f158df5aa1e89b953962f","tid":784103,"uid":94454,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"55197b89163765a99dec141e888d4fd4e9ea451e","tid":784103,"uid":28563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:19:00.000Z","msg":"留名睇0愛心child登仔屌人戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"上面已經有個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3a7efbd1dd55f3a29c7432d425c29f7f0aad26","tid":784103,"uid":65128,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72261c27685fb9957a3495c09ad253cd4a1d0336","tid":784103,"uid":28450,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67460a33ba9124020a57cfdcb0364c6bad47a89c","tid":784103,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":14,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:09:42.000Z","msg":"寵物撚寧舍戇鳩 搞咩善終呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"人地有錢做關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33949e2d33286bbc9a80821ee09546de19bb3027","tid":784103,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:29:10.000Z","msg":"個模fail 左咪搵第二隻同品種既及多次模囉"},{"pid":"20de00620da7537c6a1cfdd9e0f580c3744179d7","tid":784103,"uid":143454,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:37:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}